{"tid":2349633,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"逾2千人參予西北部地下瘋狂派對，法國警方阻止爆衝突。在警察包圍下，派對仍然通宵進行！","createTime":"2021-01-01T16:32:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-01T16:40:45.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"491d92496810bebb537a6d260fca79e80921ff99","tid":2349633,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T16:32:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1568240-20210102.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1568240-20210102.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=3ylU62tgaeYkhBfBjxJ1gbeFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=0054c5f7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1568240-20210102.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=3817e201\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1568240-20210102.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n法國警方透露，約2500人參予西北部一個地下瘋狂派對，與到場警察發生衝突。<br />\n<br />\n這批人由法國不同地方抵埗，在西北部城市雷恩以南的空置貨倉內舉行瘋狂派對，但受部分地區人士試圖阻止。參予派對的人士投擲玻璃樽及石塊回應，又焚燒汽車。到場的警察阻止派對舉行，雙方衝突，據報有警員受傷。目擊者表示，在警方包圍下，這個瘋狂派對仍通宵進行。<br />\n<br />\n法國為防範新型肺炎疫情傳播，除夕及元旦仍實施宵禁，又動員10萬警力，打擊派對活動。"},{"pid":"0317b28f83719f0ae8f35a8b4130833597b61fa9","tid":2349633,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T16:38:40.000Z","msg":"舞照跳"},{"pid":"601043fddab2bf97007bb4c2d1c4ae2cfe3a7f48","tid":2349633,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T16:40:45.000Z","msg":"cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}